c: 30
v: 9
t: "Koo shibachendakhwo khushialo tawe balola shingala indukho yabalia baliho imbeli wabu, bali aba amaani amaanji okhubashila…nebalimanga emikunda nibachikasia po okhubashila bo, shingabalimanga, ne Abarumwa babu babetsela nende ebifune biahabulafu, kho Nyasaye shiyali wokhuba kholela obubii tawe halali abeene nibo bekholela obubii"